  "description": "PromptPanel is an open-source native macOS prompt manager and snippet launcher for AI power users. It stores prompts locally in SQLite, opens a keyboard-first global hotkey panel, and pastes reusable prompts, code snippets, templates, and instructions into ChatGPT, Claude, Cursor, Copilot, VS Code, Terminal, browsers, or any focused text field.",
